      "text": "Nelli na Mattu walikuwa wakicheza katika shamba dogo. ​‟Nelli”, mama aliita. ‟Mchukue ndugu yako na mwelekee kuchota maji. Nahitaji kumwosha mtoto”",
      "audio": [
        {
          "src": "https://s3.amazonaws.com/BloomLibraryBooks/michaelshuji101%40gmail.com%2f9c44bcde-d201-4b08-8821-20e3b1f712df%2fFamilia+Yajifunza+Chanjo%2faudio%2fi7dd6310f-37fe-43d4-936a-fe75763f73b8.mp3",
          "dur": 13.191837
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "n": 2,
      "img": "https://s3.amazonaws.com/BloomLibraryBooks/michaelshuji101%40gmail.com%2f9c44bcde-d201-4b08-8821-20e3b1f712df%2fFamilia+Yajifunza+Chanjo%2fpage+2.jpg",
      "text": "Nelli na nduguye walichukua vibuyu na kuelekea kuyachota maji kidimbwini. Huko walimwona mwanadada wasiyemjua. Alikuwa akiwazungumzia waliokuwa wakichota maji.",
      "audio": [
        {
          "src": "https://s3.amazonaws.com/BloomLibraryBooks/michaelshuji101%40gmail.com%2f9c44bcde-d201-4b08-8821-20e3b1f712df%2fFamilia+Yajifunza+Chanjo%2faudio%2fbb3135ff-a67d-4921-889d-bc2615b231d8.mp3",
          "dur": 13.897143
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "n": 3,
      "img": "https://s3.amazonaws.com/BloomLibraryBooks/michaelshuji101%40gmail.com%2f9c44bcde-d201-4b08-8821-20e3b1f712df%2fFamilia+Yajifunza+Chanjo%2fpage+3.jpg",
      "text": "Nelli alianza kuvijaza vibuyu maji. Wakati huo, mwanadada huyo akamwambia, \"Hujambo, Mimi ni nesi Kerol kutoka kwenye kliniki. Waitwa nani?\"",
      "audio": [
        {
          "src": "https://s3.amazonaws.com/BloomLibraryBooks/michaelshuji101%40gmail.com%2f9c44bcde-d201-4b08-8821-20e3b1f712df%2fFamilia+Yajifunza+Chanjo%2faudio%2fca45212c-7d72-483a-8339-933845b2bb79.mp3",
          "dur": 13.400816
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "n": 4,
      "img": "https://s3.amazonaws.com/BloomLibraryBooks/michaelshuji101%40gmail.com%2f9c44bcde-d201-4b08-8821-20e3b1f712df%2fFamilia+Yajifunza+Chanjo%2fpage+4.jpg",
      "text": "Nelli akamjibu, \"Naitwa Nelli na huyu ni Mattu. Tunamchotea mama yetu maji ili akamwoshe dada yetu mdogo\".\n\"Nyinyi ni wasaidiza wema. Naweza wasaidia kuyabeba maji nyumbani? Ningependa kuzungumza na mama yenu?\"",
      "audio": [
        {
          "src": "https://s3.amazonaws.com/BloomLibraryBooks/michaelshuji101%40gmail.com%2f9c44bcde-d201-4b08-8821-20e3b1f712df%2fFamilia+Yajifunza+Chanjo%2faudio%2fi4cfb116d-2298-4c90-a053-261bd81eed10.mp3",
          "dur": 19.487347
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "n": 5,
      "img": "https://s3.amazonaws.com/BloomLibraryBooks/michaelshuji101%40gmail.com%2f9c44bcde-d201-4b08-8821-20e3b1f712df%2fFamilia+Yajifunza+Chanjo%2fpage+7.jpg",
      "text": "Wote walitembea pamoja wakielekea kwa nyumba. Walipokuwa karibu kufika nyumbani, Nelli aliita kwa sauti, \"Mama, mama! Kuna mtu hapa anayetaka kukuona.\"",
      "audio": [
        {
          "src": "https://s3.amazonaws.com/BloomLibraryBooks/michaelshuji101%40gmail.com%2f9c44bcde-d201-4b08-8821-20e3b1f712df%2fFamilia+Yajifunza+Chanjo%2faudio%2fi899b8465-a63f-4cfe-9d40-b2656ac02d28.mp3",
          "dur": 15.595102
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "n": 6,
      "img": "https://s3.amazonaws.com/BloomLibraryBooks/michaelshuji101%40gmail.com%2f9c44bcde-d201-4b08-8821-20e3b1f712df%2fFamilia+Yajifunza+Chanjo%2fpage+8.jpg",
      "text": "Mama alikuja mlangoni huku akibeba mtoto.\n\"Hujambo Nelli, namjua rafiki yako mgeni. Alikulia kijiji jirani na chetu. Karibu nyumbani mwetu, Kerol.\"",
      "audio": [
        {
          "src": "https://s3.amazonaws.com/BloomLibraryBooks/michaelshuji101%40gmail.com%2f9c44bcde-d201-4b08-8821-20e3b1f712df%2fFamilia+Yajifunza+Chanjo%2faudio%2faef01171-389c-47f8-894e-eb71be0958f2.mp3",
          "dur": 4.205714
